show.description: When betrayal strikes at the heart of a family business, one father's quest for revenge leads his daughter into the dangerous world of the mafia. After his best friend and partner's treachery, Bianca's father makes a desperate deal with Don Pedro, a ruthless Mafia Lord—leaving his daughter behind as collateral. Caught in this high-stakes power play, Bianca finds an unexpected ally in Enzo, Don Pedro's principled son who's been secretly enchanted with her since their first encounter. As Enzo's disgust for his father's empire grows, the two forge a passionate alliance and elaborate escape plan. But in a world where loyalty is currency and deception runs deep, their dangerous charade of love might become something far more real—and deadly.
